Change Log
==========

Version 1.0 (roadmap)
---------------------
- Create REST resource objects
- Add resource caching
- Add resource authentication
- Create documentation
- Create website
- Add Application Loader class
    - Implement resource loader
- Implement attribute validators
    - Integer
    - Text
    - Email
    - Date
    - ForeignKey
- Add Application Config class
    - Implement service global config options
    - Implement resource specific config options
- Add regex routing (config routes)


Version 0.4.3 (planned)
-----------------------
+ Authorization
    + None
    + Basic
    + Digest
- Authentification configuration
    - Global configuration
    - Resource specific configuration


Version 0.4.2 (13-01-2012)
==========================
+ Add Application Router [feature-app-router]
    + Simple routing (dir structure)
+ Implement HTTP Request class [feature-http-request]
+ Implement HTTP Header class [feature-http-header]
    + Add HTTP status codes
    + Accept


Version 0.4.1 (03-01-2012)
==========================
+ Implement HTTP accept (format) header [feature-http-accept]
+ Refactor passing request & response objects [refactor-request-response]
+ Add unit tests for resource components [feature-more-tests]
    + display
    + manager
    + factory


Version 0.4 (29-12-2011)
------------------------
+ Setup unit test structure [concept-unit-tests]
+ Refactor simple router class
+ Implement http methods [feature-http-methods]
    + POST
    + PUT
    + DELETE
+ Add HTTP status codes
+ Add unit tests for resource components [concept-unit-tests]
    + component
    + data
    + format


Version 0.3 (28-12-2011)
------------------------
+ Refactor Collection and Item abstract classes to use the same interface [refactor-collection]
+ Rename formatter to display [refactor-display]
+ Rename representation to format [refactor-format]
+ Refactor Resource class to use a manager class [concept-resource-manager]
+ Create a resource factory class [concept-resource-factory]


Version 0.2 (22-12-2011)
------------------------
+ Add an application abstract class
+ Create demo resource: blog post
+ Implement HTTP headers
    + Content type


Version 0.1 (18-12-2011)
========================
+ Concept resource structure
+ Multiple representations (Json, Xml)
+ Add resource configuration options
+ Add logger instance
